NAME: Double Slap
DESCRIPTION: Hits opponent 2 - 5 times in a row.

NAME: Hyper Beam
DESCRIPTION: The user must recharge after use.

NAME: Super Fang
DESCRIPTION: Always takes off half of the target's HP.

NAME: Fire Fang
DESCRIPTION: Chance to burn the target, or cause it to flinch.

NAME: V-create
DESCRIPTION: Lowers the user's defense, special defense, and speed.

NAME: Fusion Flare
DESCRIPTION: Power increases if Fusion Bolt is used in the same turn.

NAME: Muddy Water
DESCRIPTION: Chance to lower the target's accuracy.

NAME: Waterfall
DESCRIPTION: Chance to cause target to flinch.

NAME: Charge
DESCRIPTION: Raises user's special defense. Electric moves are stronger next turn.

NAME: Fusion Bolt
DESCRIPTION: Power increases if Fusion Flare is used in the same turn.

NAME: Charge Beam
DESCRIPTION: Chance to raise user's special attack.

NAME: Absorb
DESCRIPTION: User recovers hald the damage inflicted on target.

NAME: Mega Drain
DESCRIPTION: User recovers hald the damage inflicted on target.

NAME: Giga Drain
DESCRIPTION: User recovers hald the damage inflicted on target.

NAME: Grass Knot
DESCRIPTION: The heavier the target, the stronger the attack.

NAME: Synthesis
DESCRIPTION: Heals user's HP. Healing varies in weather.
